```

### Duplicate Value Formatting
```typescript
// ‚ùå DON'T: Manually format values
if (typeof value === "boolean") {
  return value ? "Yes" : "No";
}
if (typeof value === "number") {
  return value.toString();
}

// ‚úÖ DO: Use existing utility
